					<description><!--[CDATA[<p-->ROCHESTER, Minn. — Mayo Clinic Comprehensive Cancer Center researchers will present their latest radiation oncology findings at the 2025 American Society for Radiation Oncology (ASTRO) Annual Meeting, scheduled to be held Sept. 27–Oct. 1 at the Moscone Center in San Francisco. The ASTRO Annual Meeting is recognized as the largest radiation oncology gathering in the […]<p></p>
